<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1079] Rename omitTf to omitTermFreqAndPositions</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1079</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1561&quot; title=&quot;Maybe rename Field.omitTf, and strengthen the javadocs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LUCENE-1561&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUCENE-1561&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; has renamed omitTf.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/376c1c12dd464164/lucene_1561_and_omittf&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/376c1c12dd464164/lucene_1561_and_omittf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
